<l n="c"><lb n="D16"/><unclear>na pre</unclear>ṣitavyā Iha karmma-kārāḥ <space/></l>
<l n="d">karādi-dāneṣu na cānya-kāryye</l>
</lg>
                   <lg n="45" met="upajāti">
<l n="a"><lb n="D17"/><unclear><g type="circleTarget">.</g> pra</unclear>ty-agradoṣā Api dehinas te <supplied reason="omitted"><space/></supplied></l>
<l n="b">na daṇ<choice><orig>d</orig><corr>ḍ</corr></choice>anīyā Iha ye praviṣṭ<unclear>āḥ</unclear></l>
<l n="c"><lb n="D18"/><unclear>te daṇ</unclear><choice><orig>d</orig><corr>ḍ</corr></choice>anīyās tu na marṣaṇīyā <supplied reason="omitted"><space/></supplied></l>
